# OneDrive/Azure App Registration Configuration
# You need to create an Azure App Registration and replace this with your actual client ID
VITE_AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-azure-app-client-id-here

# Instructions to get your Azure Client ID:
# 1. Go to https://portal.azure.com
# 2. Navigate to "Azure Active Directory" > "App registrations"
# 3. Click "New registration"
# 4. Fill in:
#    - Name: "Web Photo Frame OneDrive Integration"
#    - Supported account types: "Accounts in any organizational directory and personal Microsoft accounts"
#    - Redirect URI: "Single-page application (SPA)" with value "http://localhost:5173" (for development)
# 5. After creation, copy the "Application (client) ID" and replace the value above
# 6. Go to "API permissions" and add:
#    - Microsoft Graph > Delegated permissions > Files.Read
#    - Microsoft Graph > Delegated permissions > Files.Read.All
#    - Microsoft Graph > Delegated permissions > User.Read
# 7. Click "Grant admin consent" if you're an admin, or ask an admin to do it
